::Reptilica/DevilDuer::

Reptilica looks up at Feline. It was a bit annoying to talk to a bot who was 
hanging a dozen feet above in a branch. He wished she'd come down.

"I'm with the Alliance, the superior faction. Which faction are you part of?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Cloaked, DevilDuer looks at Feline from behind a few bushes. If she made any 
move to attack Reptilica, she would regret it very soon. He holds his stun 
gun ready, not making any noise as he looks for any sign of trouble.
